<div class="container">
  <h1>Welcome to Tourist Spots</h1>
  <h2>Experience the true beauty of Japan, beyond filters.</h2>

    <p>Do you know the truly amazing tourist spots?</p>
    <p>Japan has many excellent tourist spots that are not generally known. Discover real tourist spots without the filters of SNS and TV.</p>

  <div class="feature">
    <h3>Feature ①: Search</h3>
    <p>Use the search function to find your favorite spots.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature">
    <h3>Feature ②: Review</h3>
    <p>When you actually visit a spot, post your real voice in response to other people's posts.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature">
    <h3>Feature ③: Post</h3>
    <p>If you find a spot that is just for you, be sure to post it.</p>
  </div>
  
  <% unless logged_in? %>
    <%= link_to "Join our community", login_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
  <% end %>
</div>